\begin_inset Formula $g$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $h$
\end_inset

 in 
\begin_inset Formula $G$
\end_inset

,
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\phi\left(gh\right)=\phi\left(g\right)\phi\left(h\right).
\]

\end_inset


