 & = & \phi\left(b\right)\phi\left(a\right).
\end{eqnarray*}

\end_inset

But then 
\begin_inset Formula $\phi\left(b\right)$
\end_inset

 is the inverse of 
\begin_inset Formula $\phi\left(a\right)$
\end_inset

 so that 
\begin_inset Formula $\phi\left(a^{-1}\right)=\phi\left(a\right)^{-1}$
\end_inset

.
