\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Next consider the following Cayley table for the group formed by 
\begin_inset Formula $\left\{ 1,-1,i,-1\right\} $
\end_inset

of the fourth roots of unity:
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\begin{array}{|c|c|c|c|c|}
